          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2493037918" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6585226474021816393">In this introduction to Detective Sargent Rebus, the police are investigating the abduction and murders of four young girls who seemingly have nothing in common to connect them to each other, or to a potential suspect. Rebus is brought in to the expanded team after the first two bodies are found.<br/><br/>In the meantime, Rebus is dealing with much more personal demons: a military past that haunts him, a daughter that he gets to visit according to the divorce visitation schedule, and the receipt of severa</span>
  <span id="freeText6585226474021816393" style="display:none">In this introduction to Detective Sargent Rebus, the police are investigating the abduction and murders of four young girls who seemingly have nothing in common to connect them to each other, or to a potential suspect. Rebus is brought in to the expanded team after the first two bodies are found.<br /><br />In the meantime, Rebus is dealing with much more personal demons: a military past that haunts him, a daughter that he gets to visit according to the divorce visitation schedule, and the receipt of several anonymous messages.<br /><br />The plot is well-paced and the characters are interesting. A great beginning for a series.</span>
